									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about Universalism in religion and theology.  For other uses of the word, see <a href="/wiki/Universalism_(disambiguation)" title="Universalism (disambiguation)">Universalism (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
